# Social Vision Agents — API Test Requests
# Use with JetBrains HTTP Client or VSCode REST Client

### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

### Trigger weekly content generation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/run
Accept: application/json

### Trigger for a specific week
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/run?week=2026-W13
Accept: application/json

### Check status of a weekly run
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/status/2026-W13
Accept: application/json

### Approve all posts (resume graph after review)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/approve/2026-W13
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{}